  "commit_message": "[IFRT] Add a `BasicBundle` as a simple portable `Bundle` implementation\n\nThis change implements `xla::ifrt::BasicBundle`, which is a simple wrapper data structure that provides `Bundle` functionality by keeping a vector `ArrayRef` internally. This is intended for a stop-gap for IFRT runtimes to provide basic `Bundle` compatibility without actual performance benefits until they natively support `Bundle` by defining their own `Bundle` subclass.\n\nPiperOrigin-RevId: 926333822",
